{"heading":"Cyrus will free the captives of Israel from Babylon—Come unto Jehovah (Christ) and be saved—To Him every knee will bow and every tongue will take an oath.","number":45,"verseCount":25,"verses":[[1,["Thus saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," to his ",["anointed",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Foreordination","tg/foreordination"],"."]]],", to ",["Cyrus",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Governments","tg/governments"],"."]]],", whose right hand I have ",["holden",["study-note-ref","c",["OR strengthened."]]],", to ",["subdue",["study-note-ref","d",[["Isa. 41:2","ot/isa/41.2"],"; ",["Dan. 5:30","ot/dan/5.30"],"."]]]," nations before him; and I will loose the loins of kings, to open before him the ",["two leaved gates",["study-note-ref","e",["OR double doors."]]],"; and the gates shall not be shut;"]],[2,["I will go before thee, and make the ",["crooked",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 40:4","ot/isa/40.4"],"."]]]," places straight: I will ",["break",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 107:16","ot/ps/107.16"],"."]]]," in pieces the gates of brass, and cut in sunder the bars of iron:"]],[3,["And I will give thee the ",["treasures of darkness",["study-note-ref","a",["OR hidden treasures (probably of Babylonia). ",["Jer. 50:37","ot/jer/50.37"],"; ",["51:13","ot/jer/51.13"],"."]]],", and hidden riches of secret places, that thou mayest know that I, the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", which call ",["thee",["clarity-word"]]," by thy ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ex. 33:12 (12, 17)","ot/ex/33.12"],"; ",["JS—H 1:33 (17, 33, 49)","pgp/js-h/1.33"],"."]]],", ",["am",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["God",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 29:23","ot/isa/29.23"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:14","bofm/3-ne/11.14"],"; ",["D&C 36:1","dc-testament/dc/36.1"],"; ",["127:3","dc-testament/dc/127.3"],"."]]]," of Israel."]],[4,["For Jacob my ",["servant’s",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 44:1 (1–2)","ot/isa/44.1"],", ",["21","ot/isa/44.21"],"; ",["1 Ne. 20:20","bofm/1-ne/20.20"],"."]]]," sake, and Israel mine ",["elect",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Election","tg/election"],"."]]],", I have even ",["called",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Governments","tg/governments"],"."]]]," thee by thy name: I have surnamed thee, though thou hast not known me."]],[5,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],["I am",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 44:8","ot/isa/44.8"],"; ",["46:9","ot/isa/46.9"],"; ",["2 Ne. 6:7","bofm/2-ne/6.7"],"; ",["3 Ne. 24:6","bofm/3-ne/24.6"],"; ",["Moses 1:6","pgp/moses/1.6"],"."]]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none else, ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," no God beside me: I girded thee, though thou hast not known me:"]],[6,["That they may know from the ",["rising",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mal. 1:11","ot/mal/1.11"],"."]]]," of the sun, and from the west, that ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none beside me. I ",["am",["clarity-word"]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none else."]],[7,["I form the ",["light",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Light [noun]","tg/light-noun"],"."]]],", and create darkness: I make peace, and create ",["evil",["study-note-ref","b",[["Amos 3:6","ot/amos/3.6"],"; ",["Alma 5:40","bofm/alma/5.40"],"; ",["Moro. 7:12","bofm/moro/7.12"],"."]]],": I the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," do all these ",["things.",["clarity-word"]]]],[8,["Drop down, ye heavens, from above, and let the skies pour down ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],": let the earth open, and let ",["them",["study-note-ref","b",["IE the heavens and the earth."]]]," bring forth ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Book of Mormon","tg/book-of-mormon"],"."]]],", and let righteousness spring up together; I the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," have created it."]],[9,["Woe unto him that ",["striveth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Job 9:3 (1–4)","ot/job/9.3"],"; ",["Eccl. 6:10","ot/eccl/6.10"],"; ",["Jacob 4:10","bofm/jacob/4.10"],"."]]]," with his ",["Maker",["study-note-ref","b",[["Hosea 8:14","ot/hosea/8.14"],"."]]],"! ",["Let",["clarity-word"]]," the potsherd ",["strive",["clarity-word"]]," with the potsherds of the earth. Shall the ",["clay",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 29:16","ot/isa/29.16"],"; ",["64:8","ot/isa/64.8"],"; ",["Jer. 18:6","ot/jer/18.6"],"; ",["Rom. 9:21","nt/rom/9.21"],"."]]]," say to him that fashioneth it, What makest thou? or thy work, He hath no hands?"]],[10,["Woe unto him that saith unto ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," father, What begettest thou? or to ",["the woman",["study-note-ref","a",["IE his mother."]]],", What hast thou brought forth?"]],[11,["Thus saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", the Holy One of Israel, and his Maker, Ask me of things to come concerning my ",["sons",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"."]]],", and concerning the ",["work",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 29:23","ot/isa/29.23"],"."]]]," of my hands ",["command ye me",["study-note-ref","c",["IE ask me what you want to know."]]],"."]],[12,["I have ",["made",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Creator","tg/jesus-christ-creator"],"."]]]," the earth, and ",["created",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Man, Physical Creation of","tg/man-physical-creation-of"],"."]]]," man upon it: I, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," my hands, have stretched out the heavens, and all their ",["host",["study-note-ref","c",[["Gen. 2:1","ot/gen/2.1"],"."]]]," have I commanded."]],[13,["I have raised ",["him",["study-note-ref","a",["IE Cyrus."]]]," up in righteousness, and I will direct all his ways: he shall ",["build",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 44:28","ot/isa/44.28"],"."]]]," my city, and he shall let go my captives, not for ",["price",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 52:3","ot/isa/52.3"],"."]]]," nor reward, saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," of hosts."]],[14,["Thus saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", The labour of ",["Egypt",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 43:3","ot/isa/43.3"],"."]]],", and merchandise of Ethiopia and of the Sabeans, men of stature, shall come over unto thee, and they shall be thine: they shall come ",["after",["study-note-ref","b",["OR behind."]]]," thee; in chains they shall come over, and they shall fall down unto thee, they shall make supplication unto thee, ",["saying,",["clarity-word"]]," Surely God ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," in thee; and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["none",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moses 1:6","pgp/moses/1.6"],"."]]]," else, ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," no God."]],[15,["Verily thou ",["art",["clarity-word"]]," a God that ",["hidest",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 38:7 (7–8)","dc-testament/dc/38.7"],"."]]]," thyself, O God of Israel, the ",["Saviour",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Savior","tg/jesus-christ-savior"],"; ",["Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]],"."]],[16,["They shall be ashamed, and also confounded, all of them: they shall go to confusion together ",["that are",["clarity-word"]]," makers of ",["idols",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Idolatry","tg/idolatry"],"."]]],"."]],[17,[["But",["clarity-word"]]," Israel shall be ",["saved",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 35:25","dc-testament/dc/35.25"],"; ",["38:33","dc-testament/dc/38.33"],"."]]]," in the ",[[["Lord",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah","tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"],"."]]],["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," with an everlasting ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Salvation, Plan of","tg/salvation-plan-of"],"."]]],": ye shall not be ashamed nor confounded world without end."]],[18,["For thus saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," that ",["created",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Creator","tg/jesus-christ-creator"],"."]]]," the heavens; God himself that formed the earth and made it; he hath established it, he created it not in vain, he formed it to be ",["inhabited",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Earth, Purpose of","tg/earth-purpose-of"],"."]]],": I ",["am",["clarity-word"]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"; and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none else."]],[19,["I have not spoken in ",["secret",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 48:16","ot/isa/48.16"],"; ",["D&C 1:34","dc-testament/dc/1.34"],"."]]],", in a dark place of the earth: I said not unto the seed of Jacob, Seek ye me in vain: I the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," speak ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 119:138","ot/ps/119.138"],"; ",["D&C 67:9","dc-testament/dc/67.9"],"."]]],", I declare things that are ",["right",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 25:28 (28–29)","bofm/2-ne/25.28"],"; ",["D&C 3:2","dc-testament/dc/3.2"],"."]]],"."]],[20,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"Assemble yourselves and come; draw near together, ye ",["that are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["escaped",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 46:3","ot/isa/46.3"],"."]]]," of the ",["nations",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Conversion","tg/conversion"],"; ",["Israel, Mission of","tg/israel-mission-of"],"."]]],": they have no ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 44:18 (18–19)","ot/isa/44.18"],"."]]]," that set up the wood of their graven image, and ",["pray",["study-note-ref","d",[["Isa. 46:7","ot/isa/46.7"],"."]]]," unto a god ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," cannot save."]],[21,["Tell ye, and bring ",["them",["clarity-word"]]," near; yea, let them take counsel together: who hath declared this from ancient time? ",["who",["clarity-word"]]," hath told it from that time? ",["have",["clarity-word"]]," not I the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"? and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," no God else beside me; a ",["just",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Justice of","tg/god-justice-of"],"; ",["Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]]," God and a ",["Saviour",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah","tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"],"; ",["Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]],"; ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none beside me."]],[22,[["Look",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 6:36","dc-testament/dc/6.36"],"; ",["43:34","dc-testament/dc/43.34"],"."]]]," unto me, and be ye ",["saved",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Salvation, Plan of","tg/salvation-plan-of"],"."]]],", all the ends of the earth: for I ",["am",["clarity-word"]]," God, and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none else."]],[23,["I have sworn by myself, the word is gone out of my mouth ",["in",["clarity-word"]]," righteousness, and shall not return, That unto me every ",["knee",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 14:11","nt/rom/14.11"],"; ",["Philip. 2:10","nt/philip/2.10"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," shall bow, every tongue shall ",["swear",["study-note-ref","b",["OR take an oath, or covenant. ",["Deut. 6:13","ot/deut/6.13"],"."]]],"."]],[24,["Surely, shall ",["one",["clarity-word"]]," say, in the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," have I righteousness and ",["strength",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 17:3","bofm/1-ne/17.3"],"; ",["Alma 26:12","bofm/alma/26.12"],"; ",["D&C 113:8 (7–8)","dc-testament/dc/113.8"],"."]]],": ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," to him shall ",["men",["clarity-word"]]," come; and all that are incensed against him shall be ashamed."]],[25,["In the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," shall all the seed of Israel be ",["justified",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Justification","tg/justification"],"."]]],", and shall glory."]]],"volume":"ot"}